<section class="pdp-benefits section section--full-width" data-pdp-benefits>
  <div class="pdp-benefits__inner">
    <header class="pdp-benefits__header">
      <div class="pdp-benefits__badge">
        {{ section.settings.badge_icon_svg }}
        {{ section.settings.badge_text }}
      </div>
      <h2 class="pdp-benefits__title">{{ section.settings.title_line_1 }}<br><span>{{ section.settings.title_line_2 }}</span></h2>
      <p class="pdp-benefits__subtitle">{{ section.settings.subtitle }}</p>
    </header>

    <div class="pdp-benefits__grid">
      {% if section.blocks.size > 0 %}
        {% for block in section.blocks %}
          <article class="pdp-benefits__card" {{ block.shopify_attributes }}>
            <div class="pdp-benefits__card-bg"></div>
            <div class="pdp-benefits__card-content">
              <div class="pdp-benefits__icon {{ block.settings.icon_color_class }}">
                {{ block.settings.icon_svg }}
              </div>
              <p class="pdp-benefits__label">{{ block.settings.problem_label }}</p>
              <h3 class="pdp-benefits__problem">{{ block.settings.problem_title }}</h3>
              <div class="pdp-benefits__divider"></div>
              <p class="pdp-benefits__label pdp-benefits__label--solution">{{ block.settings.solution_label }}</p>
              <h4 class="pdp-benefits__solution">{{ block.settings.solution_title }}</h4>
              <p class="pdp-benefits__description">{{ block.settings.description }}</p>
              <div class="pdp-benefits__stat">
                <span class="pdp-benefits__stat-number {{ block.settings.stat_color_class }}">{{ block.settings.stat_value }}</span>
                <span>{{ block.settings.stat_label }}</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
        {% endfor %}
      {% else %}
        <article class="pdp-benefits__card"><div class="pdp-benefits__card-bg"></div><div class="pdp-benefits__card-content"><div class="pdp-benefits__icon pdp-benefits__icon--orange"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M8.5 14.5A2.5 2.5 0 0 0 11 12c0-1.38-.5-2-1-3-1.072-2.143-.224-4.054 2-6 .5 2.5 2 4.9 4 6.5 2 1.6 3 3.5 3 5.5a7 7 0 1 1-14 0c0-1.153.433-2.294 1-3a2.5 2.5 0 0 0 2.5 2.5z"></path></svg></div><p class="pdp-benefits__label">EL PROBLEMA</p><h3 class="pdp-benefits__problem">Pasas horas en el gimnasio con resultados minimos?</h3><div class="pdp-benefits__divider"></div><p class="pdp-benefits__label pdp-benefits__label--solution">LA SOLUCION</p><h4 class="pdp-benefits__solution">Quema mas de 1.000 calorias por hora</h4><p class="pdp-benefits__description">La cuerda para saltar quema mas calorias que correr, montar en bicicleta o la mayoria de los entrenamientos de gimnasio en la mitad del tiempo. Consigue un entrenamiento de cardio de cuerpo completo que da resultados reales, rapido.</p><div class="pdp-benefits__stat"><span class="pdp-benefits__stat-number pdp-benefits__stat-number--orange">1,000</span><span>calorias/hora</span></div></div></article>
        <article class="pdp-benefits__card"><div class="pdp-benefits__card-bg"></div><div class="pdp-benefits__card-content"><div class="pdp-benefits__icon pdp-benefits__icon--purple"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12s-8-6-8-12a8 8 0 0 1 16 0Z"></path><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle></svg></div><p class="pdp-benefits__label">EL PROBLEMA</p><h3 class="pdp-benefits__problem">Cansado de desplazarte a gimnasios llenos?</h3><div class="pdp-benefits__divider"></div><p class="pdp-benefits__label pdp-benefits__label--solution">LA SOLUCION</p><h4 class="pdp-benefits__solution">Entrena donde quieras, cuando quieras</h4><p class="pdp-benefits__description">No necesitas membresia de gimnasio. Tu cuerda cabe en tu bolsa y funciona en cualquier lugar: casa, parque, habitacion de hotel o patio. Libertad total de entrenamiento en tu bolsillo.</p><div class="pdp-benefits__stat"><span class="pdp-benefits__stat-number pdp-benefits__stat-number--purple">10 min</span><span>para empezar</span></div></div></article>
        <article class="pdp-benefits__card"><div class="pdp-benefits__card-bg"></div><div class="pdp-benefits__card-content"><div class="pdp-benefits__icon pdp-benefits__icon--green"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true"><path d="M19 7V4a1 1 0 0 0-1-1H5a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h15a1 1 0 0 1 1 1v4h-3a2 2 0 0 0 0 4h3a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-2a1 1 0 0 0-1-1"></path><path d="M3 5v14a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h15a1 1 0 0 0 1-1v-4"></path></svg></div><p class="pdp-benefits__label">EL PROBLEMA</p><h3 class="pdp-benefits__problem">Gastas dinero en membresias de gimnasio costosas?</h3><div class="pdp-benefits__divider"></div><p class="pdp-benefits__label pdp-benefits__label--solution">LA SOLUCION</p><h4 class="pdp-benefits__solution">Inversion unica, resultados de por vida</h4><p class="pdp-benefits__description">Cancela tu membresia mensual. Esta es una compra unica que se paga rapidamente, sin cuotas recurrentes.</p><div class="pdp-benefits__stat"><span class="pdp-benefits__stat-number pdp-benefits__stat-number--green">EUR 0</span><span>cuotas mensuales</span></div></div></article>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
